+    	echo 'export NIX_PATH=nixpkgs=/home/---<USERNAME>---/nixpkgs' >> ~/.bashrc
+    	export NIX_PATH=nixpkgs=/home/---<USERNAME>---/nixpkgs
 
-There are two ways to get a source tree:
